I don't have any memory of previous conversations with you. Each conversation I have starts fresh without access to prior interactions or any code you may have asked me to remember in the past.

If you'd like me to work with specific code now, you can:
1. Share the code directly with me in this conversation
2. Ask me to work with files in the current project directory (which I can read and modify)
3. Provide context about what you'd like to do with code

Feel free to share any code you'd like help with!
